## Bio 👩🏽‍🔬👩🏽‍💻

<p>I am a PhD student in neuroscience working in the [Neurogenesis & Neurodegeneration lab](https://nin.nl/research/researchgroups/salta-group/) at the Netherlands Institute for Neuroscience 🇳🇱. <br>
I am a molecular biologist by training, trying to dig into some single cell RNA-sequencing datasets (and having fun creating this website!).
My main interests are adult hippocampal neurogenesis, Alzheimer's disease and non-coding RNAs. <p>
...Good food, good books, sports and fighting for equal rights and a sustainable future make me happy. 

<br>

